address.streetAddress: Chelsea Plan, The Manors at Riley's Meadow

location.fullValue: Chelsea Plan, The Manors at Riley's Meadow

data.description: Welcome to a truly one-of-a-kind gem in charming Graham! This unique 4/2.5 offers the best of both worlds. unique blend of classic charm and modern comforts. The exterior of the home has been completely transformed, new siding, fresh roof, new HVAC system offers comfort in every season and new luxury vinyl flooring has been installed in some rooms. Hardwood floors exude timeless elegance, adding character and warmth to the living space. kitchen & bathrooms, tile flooring offers a clean and practical touch. Kitchen has been updated w/ stunning granite countertops. kitchen appliances are included, so you can start cooking delicious meals right away. The outdoor spaces are equally impressive. A covered side deck provides a cozy spot to enjoy the outdoors and greet the day. A large rear deck is attached to an above-ground pool, which is less than 2 years old, ensuring hours of summer fun and relaxation. The metal carport remains to provide shelter for your vehicles.
